TITLE: Initializing ReactFlow Component in React
DESCRIPTION: Basic implementation example of the ReactFlow component showing the minimal setup with nodes, edges, and change handlers. This is the core component for creating a flow diagram in React.
SOURCE: https://github.com/xyflow/web/blob/main/sites/reactflow.dev/src/content/api-reference/react-flow.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_0

LANGUAGE: tsx
CODE:
```
import { ReactFlow } from '@xyflow/react'

export default function Flow() {
  return <ReactFlow
    nodes={...}
    edges={...}
    onNodesChange={...}
    ...
  />
}
```

