TITLE: Initializing State for Nodes and Edges in JavaScript
DESCRIPTION: This snippet sets up state variables for nodes and edges within a React component using useState. The initialNodes and initialEdges variables represent the starting data for the flow graph. This is required for interactive behavior to track and update node and edge state in React Flow.
