TITLE: Correct useReactFlow Hook Usage with External Provider (JSX)
DESCRIPTION: This snippet illustrates the correct way to use the `useReactFlow` hook. The hook is called within the `Flow` component, which is then wrapped by `<ReactFlowProvider>` in the `FlowWithProvider` parent component. This ensures the `Flow` component has access to the necessary React Flow context.
SOURCE: https://github.com/xyflow/web/blob/main/sites/reactflow.dev/src/content/learn/troubleshooting/index.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_2

