```

LANGUAGE: jsx
CODE:
```
function Flow() {\n  const nodeTypes = useMemo(() => ({ specialType: SpecialNode }), []);\n\n  return <ReactFlow nodes={[]} nodeTypes={nodeTypes} />;\n}
```

LANGUAGE: jsx
