TITLE: React Flow App Component Setup
DESCRIPTION: Main App component configuration with React Flow, including custom node type registration and store integration.
SOURCE: https://github.com/xyflow/web/blob/main/sites/reactflow.dev/src/content/learn/tutorials/react-flow-and-the-web-audio-api.mdx#2025-04-23_snippet_13

LANGUAGE: jsx
